item.title: Cauda Equina Syndrome
item.description: Cauda Equina Syndrome For as long as I can remember, I’ve had back pain leading to a sedentary lifestyle, trying to avoid the pain. Everything becomes “the pain.” Spine Nerve Root Compression Whatever you want to call it, it sucked.
